body:
@TomAugspurger FYI

seems circleci is refusing to run PR's for most folks (though your's and mine still run). maybe something changed on there side.

Yeah, I was looking into that last night. The error message isn't that informative "An error occurred while fetching information about this build from GitHub."

The doc build timed out on this since I didn't pick the commit that pinned sphinx to 1.5*. Going to wait till Appveyor finishes and then push, merge, and tag the release.
